  • Classes in fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.backend used by fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.backend 
    Class and Description
    BuilderIndexProvider
    An interface specifying an index provider builder.
    In order to follow the builder design pattern and for code reusability, an interface is used so that the implementation can be easily changed.
    ChemicalException
    ChemicalException is an exception that indicates an error inherent to the chemical library.
    This exception can be thrown for an internal error, but the user will mostly receive exception concerning a mishandling of the library.
    Solution
    Central class of the library.
    Solution.Strategy
    Different strategies available for reagent selection sequence.
    SubIndexProvider
    This interface describes the behavior of a sub index provider, used by a IndexProvider.
    SubIndexProviderSolution
    This class represents a sub index provider on a solution.
